radiographic_examinations.findings: Unremarkable liver parenchyma without masses; gallbladder had nonspecific wall thickening.
Features of autoimmune hepatitis with intensely active chronic lobular hepatitis, active interface hepatitis with plasmacytosis, and substantial bridging fibrosis.
radiographic_examinations.changes_over_time: Biopsy findings indicated progression from no fibrosis in the prior biopsy to substantial bridging fibrosis.
